{"tid":2238020,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘋果A1: O記拘9人指助偷渡 12港青家屬憂公安酷刑逼供","createTime":"2020-10-10T18:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T13:19:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c0878c8cba565b4698cc608b181f3bd5cb3f86","tid":2238020,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/121093629_10159522459432448_2601632259923732257_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=Ep3Es-da1mUAX8d9Adj&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=c353608f5eed274ed55122f6a6443267&amp;oe=5FA78B33\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F121093629_10159522459432448_2601632259923732257_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DEp3Es-da1mUAX8d9Adj%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3Dc353608f5eed274ed55122f6a6443267%26oe%3D5FA78B33&h=1a7de1ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【#蘋果頭條】12名港人疑偷渡往台灣期間被中國海警截獲，曾否認是跨境行動且事前不知情的警方，昨晨突然大搜捕，以協助罪犯罪名拘捕九人，涉為偷渡12人提供住所及價值數十萬元的船隻等。被捕者包括本土民主前線成員鍾雪瑩及社民連梁國雄前議員助理唐婉清。立法會議員涂謹申擔心內地透過酷刑逼供，得到九人的所謂「犯案」證據，家屬亦對12人可能面對的酷刑逼供深感憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/AUJMIZVN6FBVPKJM5X7YI4PPCE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FAUJMIZVN6FBVPKJM5X7YI4PPCE%2F&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUleNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=86f804c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FAUJMIZVN6FBVPKJM5X7YI4PPCE%2F&h=ab33aba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/AUJMIZVN6FBVPKJM5X7YI4PPCE/</a>"},{"pid":"92ee9c3b3ed59f90af100d488747bbc3905bef55","tid":2238020,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/